==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Unquiet
<hw>Un*qui"et</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> +
<ets>quiet</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not quiet; restless; uneasy; agitated;
disturbed.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Un*qui"et*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un*qui"et*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unquietude</ent>⟦br⟧
